description: Our agency is now online about 3 months. We have had many calls already. Our quota so far is 3:1. That means that every third guy agrees to our immoral offer. I would even say that most of the guys look nice. This time I had a call from somebody who lived in the outskirts of Prague. And indeed I have never seen a more dirty and sad place than his apartment. But the boy - something between a teenager and a young man - dammit - he looked like a model. He wore that typical ghetto-style and he even had tattoos on his hands - but his face and body. Wow. He was totally desperate. He had a problem with gambling. He owed money to friends and even the casino. An easy (but expensive) catch.
title: Debt Dandy 11
